# Evidence

## Purpose

This folder contains screenshots demonstrating the development of the Atlanta Falcons ISO 27001:2022 Risk Assessment Case Study.

The screenshots provide visual evidence of the Excel-based risk management artifacts developed throughout the project.

## Included Evidence

- Asset Register
- Threat Register
- Vulnerability Register
- Risk Assessment
- Risk Register
- Risk Treatment Plan
- Statement of Applicability
- Internal Audit Report
- Corrective Action Log

## Skills Demonstrated

- Risk Identification
- Risk Analysis
- Risk Treatment
- ISO 27001 Control Mapping
- Internal Auditing
- Corrective Action Management
- Microsoft Excel
